document_data.name: Mosque of Tyr
document_data.mainbody: The '''Mosque of Tyr''' was a temple-stronghold dedicated to the [[Tyr|Maimed God]], that was located in the [[Delimbiyr Vale]]. It was run by the [[elven]] [[priest]], [[Elorshin Floshin]].
document_data.Location: The mosque was about a two day's travel east from the town of [[Daggerford]].
document_data.Activities: It catered primarily to those individuals that were traveling along the [[Trade Way]], between Daggerford and [[Waterdeep]].
